Implementing as a transformer `!plugin`

```js !plugin type=transformer of=prettier 
export const transformer = ({node, src, codeSource, rawSource, originalSource}) => {
  const lines = src.split('\n')
  const body = lines.slice(1,-1).join('\n')
  lines[0] += " !prettied"
  return lines.join('\n')
}
```

